data.description:
Welcome to 805 Hickok Drive, a delightful residence nestled 15 minutes from Fort Hood in the heart of Killeen, TX. This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience with practical location.

As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances, granite countertops, and a convenient breakfast bar. This house is in GREAT condition and ready for IMMEDIATE move-in- you'll see it's also priced to sell!

The spacious master bedroom provides a relaxing retreat with an ensuite bathroom, ensuring a private oasis for the homeowners. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility and could be used as a home office or a guest room.

Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home is minutes from schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options. Schedule a showing today and discover the comfort and charm that 805 Hickok Drive has to offer.
